---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="about"
  description="about the downforce blog — race analysis with actual opinions"
>
  <div class="about-wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-header reveal-on-scroll">
        <div class="about-accent-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <h1 class="about-title">about</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="about-body reveal-on-scroll">
        <div class="about-bio">
          <p class="bio-lead">
            i'm a high schooler based in riyadh who has loved formula one for as long
            as i can remember. this is where i write about it.
          </p>

          <p>
            i started the downforce blog since i wanted a place to put my actual
            thoughts on races, not just repost what everyone else was saying. f1 is
            the most technically complex, politically messy, and genuinely exciting
            sport on the planet, and most coverage doesn't do it justice.
          </p>

          <p>
            i'm a massive Aston Martin fan and an even bigger Fernando Alonso fan.
            the man is the greatest driver of all time and i will not be taking
            questions. that bias shows up in the writing. so does everything else i
            think about the sport.
          </p>

          <p>
            posts go up after every race weekend, plus editorials and hot takes
            whenever something in the paddock is worth reacting to.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="about-details">
          <div class="detail-block">
            <h2 class="detail-label">what's covered</h2>
            <ul class="detail-list">
              <li>race reports after every grand prix</li>
              <li>driver and team analysis</li>
              <li>strategy breakdowns and hot takes</li>
              <li>season storylines and championship battles</li>
              <li>friday editorials on whatever's worth discussing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="detail-block">
            <h2 class="detail-label">stay updated</h2>
            <ul class="detail-list">
              <li>
                <a href="/rss.xml" class="detail-link">rss feed →</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-wrapper {
    padding-top: calc(56px + 4rem);
    padding-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-accent-line {
    width: 32px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 0.95;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .about-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr minmax(200px, 280px);
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .about-bio {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .bio-lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.625rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .about-bio p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .about-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .detail-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .detail-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .detail-list li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding-left: 0.75rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .detail-list li:hover {
    border-left-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .detail-link {
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }
  .detail-link:hover { color: var(--accent-hover); }
</style>
